body		• Forged Property Takeover: They hatched a diabolical plan to illegitimately seize the prestigious 3rd floor of Esplanade House, using forged documents to oust the rightful owners./body		• Deceptive Tactics: Saraf cunningly exploited legal loopholes, appearing to offer a mere hand loan, but covertly securing complete ownership through dubious means./body		• Fictitious Hostage Drama: Saraf spun a fictitious narrative, accusing Rao's henchmen of holding his own father hostage at gunpoint, leading to an extortion case against Rao./body		• Lavish Lifestyle and Legal Manipulation: Despite living in a lavish 150 Crore House, Saraf used cunning legal maneuvers to battle Martin Burn Ltd./body		• Public Altercation: Saraf's actions led to a public altercation with Ali Asgar Merchant, misusing Merchant's Bombay Gymkhana membership./body		• Nefarious Extortion Plot: Saraf falsely implicated Merchant and the restaurant owner, demanding a jaw-dropping 9 Crores, with his close confidant Alok Makharia involved./body		• Pursuing Justice: As an investigative journalist, I have diligently pursued this case, peeling back the layers of deception to reveal Saraf's true identity as the extortionist with underworld connections./body	/body	The demand for an impartial investigation into Abhishek Badriprasad Saraf's criminal activities is urgent. Innocent victims have suffered due to his malevolent machinations, and justice must be served. I implore you to join me in shedding light on this dark and twisted tale, bringing awareness to the community and helping the affected parties seek justice./body	Your dedication to fair and accurate reporting can make a significant difference in our pursuit of truth and accountability./body	/body	Thank you for your time and consideration./body	/body	Sincerely,/body	Santosh Sakpal/body	Phone: +91 82689 17276/body	Email: santoshsakpal03@gmail.com/body	Address: B/6 Shimgyamanohar Apartments, Thane Belapur Road, Digha West, New Mumbai 400708/body	/body	References – /body	Abhishek Saraf +91 98201 80065/body	Alok Makharia +91 98200 00179/body	Ali Asgar Merchant +91 98200 04400/body	Inspector Sanjay Taralgatti +91 81080 55100 (Anti Extortion Cell)/body	/body	DK Rao / Abhishek Saraf feud - https://www.mid-day.com/mumbai/mumbai-news/article/Mumbai--Azad-Maidan-cops-to-seek-D-K-Rao-s-custody-in-2012-case-18660162/body	/body	Martin Burn Ltd vs Abhishek Saraf - https://indiankanoon.org/doc/157591602//body	/body	Abhishek Saraf vs Ali Asgar Merchant - https://www.openpr.com/news/3119230/bombay-gymkhana-club-extortion-scandal-false-complainant/body	/body	PS - I have included a link of the heritage building Esplanade House, where Abhishek Saraf and his then partner, gangster DK Rao, unlawfully took over the 3rd floor. You can find the image attached to this email - https://www.google.com/maps/uv?pb=!1s0x3be7d1dc372089f7%3A0xe100943fe6b08ac7!3m1!7e115!4s%2Fmaps%2Fplace%2Fesplanade%2Bhouse%2F%4018.9360172%2C72.8311613%2C3a%2C75y%2C98.19h%2C90t%2Fdata%3D*213m4*211e1*213m2*211sSH702L9O0cc0327_Ouesow*212e0*214m2*213m1*211s0x3be7d1dc372089f7%3A0xe100943fe6b08ac7%3Fsa%3DX%26ved%3D2ahUKEwiViKLX4aWAAxWBbmwGHUHaCGoQpx96BAhZEAA!5sesplanade%20house%20-%20Google%20Search!15sCgIgAQ&imagekey=!1e2!2sSH702L9O0cc0327_Ouesow&hl=en&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwiViKLX4aWAAxWBbmwGHUHaCGoQpx96BAhpEAw/body	/body	/body	/body	/body	/body	/body	/sig	Santosh Sakpal /sig	(+91 82689 17276 / santoshsakpal03@gmail.com) /sig	B/6 Shimgyamanohar Apartments. /sig	Thane Belapur Road Digha West, /sig	New Mumbai 400708/sig	/recip	Zoom - Maximum Style	multimediacommunications@gmail.com	1	multimediacommunications@gmail.com	9899984998																			2023-06-23 10:08:12	2023-06-23 10:08:12		Soumya Chandel	Reporter	press/recip	ZIA HAQ	mailtozia@gmail.com	1																					2023-06-26 00:40:42	2023-06-26 00:40:42		Hindustan Times	Correspondent	press/recip	Zee news	pramodr@zeenetwork.com	1	pramodr@zeenetwork.com	9739911828										